Title: 004: Data and Strategy, Three Pillars of Research and Building your Career with Brendan Hogan
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with business strategy expert Brendan Hogan. You will learn how he uses Data to alter strategy of businesses, you will learn about the three pillars of research and how to build a successful career from your strengths.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/4
